foliation.p:
Written in brown ink in the upper right-hand corner of the recto of each leaf, but with several errors: leaf 24
                                        is foliated as '14', the numbers '49' and '92' occur twice, and a leaf has been skipped between '52' and '53;
                                        '97' and '98' [although it has been numbered with pencil as '97*' by a modern hand]; and '124' and '125'.
